Nissan Motor Corp in USA, a unitof Nissan Motor Co Ltd, said its domestic car sales for theMarch 21-31 period rose 82.8 pct to 4,635 from 2,536 a yearago.    It said automobile sales for the month gained 37.6 pct to10,130 from 7,363 and year to date they increased to 23,899from 20,209.    Nissan said late-March U.S. truck sales increased 15.5 pctto 3,567 from 3,089. The month's truck sales declined 4.2 pctto 7,271 from 7,592, and year to date, sales increased to20,398 from 18,477. Reuter&#3;